nima&lt;/a&gt; to power the forge.\nIt is time to create something magnificent.\nI have dedicated my existence here to learning the ways of the forge. Over thousands of your years I have improved my process and the result is armor unlike any other.\nI would be glad to give you a glimpse into my methods. All you need to do is listen and do exactly as I say.\nHow does that sound?\nThis armor has your mark on it, &lt;name&gt;. Cherish it, and know that it is the best it can be for where you are now.\nIn the future, you will find ways to grow.\nAre you ready to begin the armor forging process?\nThere is also a Hold the heat steady NPC visible."}
