d back to the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Earth\"&gt;Temple of Earth&lt;/a&gt;.\nAfter completing this quest along with &lt;a href=\"The%20Middle%20Fragment\"&gt;The Middle Fragment&lt;/a&gt;, Maruut Stonebinder starts the final pillar fragment quest chain: &lt;a href=\"The%20Very%20Earth%20Beneath%20Our%20Feet\"&gt;The Very Earth Beneath Our Feet&lt;/a&gt;."}
