{"id": "558971", "revid": "39299307", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=558971", "title": "The Stormwind Extraction", "text": "Objectives.\nComplete \"The Stormwind Extraction\" scenario.\nDescription.\nMy lady is shrewd indeed. If we are to infiltrate &lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20City\"&gt;Stormwind City&lt;/a&gt;, we will need the very best the &lt;a href=\"Horde\"&gt;Horde&lt;/a&gt; has to offer, and yet a team so small as to be able to infiltrate the heart of &lt;a href=\"Alliance\"&gt;Alliance&lt;/a&gt; territory unseen.\n&lt;Nathanos peers at the gathered group, stroking his chin.&gt;\nYes, I see.\nThe path ahead is clear. Speak to me when you are ready to undertake the &lt;a href=\"Sylvanas%20Windrunner\"&gt;Warchief's&lt;/a&gt; mission, &lt;name&gt;.\nRewards.\nYou will receive:\nProgress.\nWe must not fail the Warchief.\nCompletion.\nWell, here we are. &lt;a href=\"Zuldazar\"&gt;Zuldazar&lt;/a&gt;. We had better stick with &lt;a href=\"Talanji\"&gt;Talanji&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Zul\"&gt;Zul&lt;/a&gt; for now. The Warchief will be interested to know what happens next.\nNotes.\nOn accept:\nAlts can choose to speak with Nathanos again to skip the scenario: \nPlayers who wish to continue, pick up the potion, &lt;a href=\"Blightcaller%27s%20Easy%20Death\"&gt;Blightcaller's Easy Death&lt;/a&gt;:\n&lt;a href=\"Deathguard%20Malcolm\"&gt;Deathguard Malcolm&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Deathguard%20Sansa\"&gt;Deathguard Sansa&lt;/a&gt; join the party. Go near the &lt;a href=\"Bank%20of%20Orgrimmar\"&gt;Bank of Orgrimmar&lt;/a&gt; (pre-\"Shadowlands\": the Gates of Orgrimmar) where &lt;a href=\"Lasan%20Skyhorn\"&gt;Lasan Skyhorn&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Aviash\"&gt;Aviash&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Skyhorn%20Eagle\"&gt;Skyhorn Eagle&lt;/a&gt;s await.\nHop on a war eagle to begin the scenario:\nStage 2: Down the Drain.\nIf you move out of the area and attack guards, Thalyssra will teleport you to back to the sewer gate.\nInteract with two &lt;a href=\"Padlock\"&gt;Padlock&lt;/a&gt;s to open the Sewer Access Gate. Rokhan and Thalyssra jump down. Follow them to enter the &lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20Stockade\"&gt;Stormwind Stockade&lt;/a&gt;.\nStage 3: The Stockades.\nUpon arriving, Rokhan kills a &lt;a href=\"7th%20Legion%20Enforcer\"&gt;7th Legion Enforcer&lt;/a&gt; and Thalyssra blasts a &lt;a href=\"7th%20Legion%20Sharpshooter%20%28Stockade%29\"&gt;7th Legion Sharpshooter&lt;/a&gt;. Rokhan goes to pick the cell door lock.\nStart clearing a path alongside Thalyssra. Several &lt;a href=\"Jailed%20Thief\"&gt;Jailed Thieves&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Incarcerated%20Troublemaker\"&gt;Incarcerated Troublemaker&lt;/a&gt;s, and &lt;a href=\"Imprisoned%20Thug\"&gt;Imprisoned Thug&lt;/a&gt;s can be seen. Make it to the center of the dungeon to catch up with Rokhan.\nLooking at a locked Cell Door, Rokhan quickly delegates:\nStage 4: Honor and Loyalty.\nInteract with the Cell Door to unlock it. Then speak with Saurfang:\nStage 5: The Primary Objective.\nRokhan and Thalyssra run to face the remaining guards. Once they are dead, the group moves to the cell containing &lt;a href=\"Zul%20the%20Prophet\"&gt;Zul the Prophet&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Princess%20Talanji\"&gt;Princess Talanji&lt;/a&gt;.\nInteract with the Cell Door to break the lock.\nJoin them in the hall:\nFollow them to the center of the hall:\nStart attacking the battlemages and other guards, clearing to the eastern end of the stockade. In the next intersection, Mage-Commander Lyra teleports in:\nStart attacking:\nOn her death:\nEnter the last room, where a trapdoor provides Stormwind Sewer Access:\nInteract with the &lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20Sewer%20Access\"&gt;Stormwind Sewer Access&lt;/a&gt; to continue.\nStage 6: The City Stirs.\nRokhan used his power and called a &lt;a href=\"Loa\"&gt;Loa&lt;/a&gt; to stealth the group, much like a rogue's &lt;a href=\"Shroud%20of%20Concealment\"&gt;Shroud of Concealment&lt;/a&gt;. Keep in the circle, close to him during the duration. Avoid &lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20Guard%20%28Stormwind%20City%29\"&gt;Stormwind Guards&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20Knight%20%28Stormwind%20City%29\"&gt;Stormwind Knights&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"D.R.O.N.E.\"&gt;D.R.O.N.E.&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Town%20Crier%20%28Stormwind%20City%29\"&gt;Town Criers&lt;/a&gt;, and even King &lt;a href=\"Anduin%20Wrynn\"&gt;Anduin Wrynn&lt;/a&gt; himself!\nIf you leave, Rokhan will summon you.\nNearby &lt;a href=\"Stormwind%20Citizen\"&gt;Stormwind Citizen&lt;/a&gt;s and a Stormwind Guard also have dialogues\nTalk to Rokhan to begin moving:\nSpeak with Rokhan again:\nStage 7: WAY Behind Enemy Lines.\nThalyssra conjured up a barrier that deflects the attacking &lt;a href=\"Gilnean%20Mauler%20%28Stormwind%20City%29\"&gt;Gilnean Maulers&lt;/a&gt;. Talanji and Rokhan also attack the worgen. If Talanji is killed, Rezan brings her back to life.\nDefeat the Gilnean Maulers throwing themselves against Thalyrssra's shield. Once the maulers are defeated, the magic barrier is down and the group begins to run, no longer stealthed. Genn and his party will continuously walk toward the group. If he catches up, everyone will die.\nKeep killing interlopers.\nOnward, a town crier drops his torch and Zul picks it up:\nKeep moving.\nApproaching Jaina will also result in a quick death.\nContinue with the group.\nSpeak with Nathanos to continue:\nStage 8: No Diplomatic Solutions.\nThe group heads down to the harbor. Zul burns a banner. They stop by the lion statue as the path is blocked by Jaina's ice walls.\nThe &lt;a href=\"Icy%20Barrier\"&gt;Icy Barrier&lt;/a&gt; is attackable, so start breaking it.\nStage 9: The Harbor Run.\nOnce the wall is destroyed, continue with the group to the main section of the Harbor filled with &lt;a href=\"Dwarven%20Rifleman\"&gt;Dwarven Riflemen&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Gnomish%20Gyro-Engineer\"&gt;Gnomish Gyro-Engineer&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Teldrassil%20Sentinel%20%28Stormwind%20City%29\"&gt;Teldrassil Sentinels&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Exodar%20Peacekeeper%20%28BfA%29\"&gt;Exodar Peacekeepers&lt;/a&gt;, Gilnean Maulers, Stormwind Knights, and Stormwind Battlemages.\nContinue following the group, clearing a path to the docks. As the party approaches the pier, Zul holds short:\nContinue to the end of the pier. Jaina and her &lt;a href=\"Mageguard%20Elite\"&gt;Mageguard Elite&lt;/a&gt;s are there.\nFinal Stage: Fate's Cold Logic.\n\"Jaina roots the group with a Frost Nova and starts walking towards it.\"\nSpeak with Talanji to continue:\nAn ending &lt;a href=\"Battle%20for%20Azeroth%20in-game%20cinematics\"&gt;cinematic&lt;/a&gt; plays:\nFinale.\nOn the other side of the cutscene, the party arrives at the &lt;a href=\"Port%20of%20Zandalar\"&gt;Port of Zandalar&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Zuldazar\"&gt;Zuldazar&lt;/a&gt;. Talk to Nathanos to finish the quest.\nTalanji offers the followup, &lt;a href=\"Welcome%20to%20Zuldazar\"&gt;Welcome to Zuldazar&lt;/a&gt;."}
