met%20Nesingwary%20Jr.\"&gt;Hemet Nesingwary Jr.&lt;/a&gt;, like his father before him, challenges you to hunt the viscious Raptors.\nShould you return alive, and with a fang, collect your reward of the , , or .\nFinale.\nCompleting all of the above quests, Hemet Nesingwary Jr sends you off for \"the\" biggest game of all.\nRewards.\nA lot of experience, and an achievement!\nSummary.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;"}
