ee to turn it in out in the field.\nDue north are , no longer despondent, led by .\nDeliver the beer:\nFurther up the path to the northeast is the Incursion forces, led by Lyalia.\nThe Crane Wing Priests are due west in the middle of the Stoneplow Fields, led by Koro Mistalkwer:\nThe Shado-Pan can be found on the southern side of the scar close to the wall.0a\nOnce Mudmug has delivered all four:\nMudmug's quest completes automatically, so feel free to turn in the instant it's done.\nFinally, Oakenshield can be found near the end of the northern path around Stoneplow Fields, not far from the wall just north of the scarred earth. Turn in to him for The Swarm Begins."}
