{"id": "279022", "revid": "40389549", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=279022", "title": "Knee-Deep", "text": "Objectives.\nUse the Half-Burnt Torch to get to the other side of the &lt;a href=\"Undertaker%27s%20Pass\"&gt;tunnel&lt;/a&gt; beneath &lt;a href=\"Gilneas%20City\"&gt;Gilneas City&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nIt's time to pack it in, &lt;name&gt;. Most of our people have made it through\u2014it's your turn now.\nTake this torch, you're going to need it. The tunnel is full of nasty, knee-biting critters of the worst kind. Use it to keep them at bay.\nSpeak to &lt;a href=\"Krennan%20Aranas\"&gt;Krennan&lt;/a&gt; on the other side.\nRewards.\nYou will receive: \nCompletion.\nYou're here, &lt;name&gt;. Most everyone made it through, but now we're stuck here... surrounded by our own... dead!\nNotes.\nHop down the tunnel. The tunnel is full of &lt;a href=\"Graveyard%20Rat\"&gt;Graveyard Rat&lt;/a&gt;s. Pet classes should put their pets on passive or dismiss them. Put the half-burnt torch on an action bar and start swinging. It works best to swing before any rats get too close to keep damage taken to a minimum. Don't stop running!"}
