{"id": "79958", "revid": "42014766", "url": "https://wowpedia.fandom.com/wiki?curid=79958", "title": "Knight-Lord Bloodvalor", "text": "Knight-Lord Bloodvalor is a &lt;a href=\"blood%20elf\"&gt;blood elf&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"paladin\"&gt;paladin&lt;/a&gt; located in the &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Blood\"&gt;Hall of Blood&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Silvermoon%20City\"&gt;Silvermoon City&lt;/a&gt;. A member of the &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Knight\"&gt;order of Blood Knights&lt;/a&gt;, he is in charge of managing the rank-and-file paladins, typically overseeing their &lt;a href=\"The%20First%20Trial\"&gt;first&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"The%20Second%20Trial\"&gt;second&lt;/a&gt; main trials. Blood Knights that were to train as Masters received summons from &lt;a href=\"Lord%20Solanar%20Bloodwrath\"&gt;Lord Solanar Bloodwrath&lt;/a&gt; (and &lt;a href=\"Lady%20Liadrin\"&gt;Lady Liadrin&lt;/a&gt; herself before him) instead.\nHistory.\nFollowing the creation of the &lt;a href=\"Blood%20Knights\"&gt;Blood Knights&lt;/a&gt; in Year 25, Bloodvalor became a member and was seen fighting with his team of knights at &lt;a href=\"Sunsail%20Anchorage\"&gt;Sunsail Anchorage&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dawnstar%20Spire\"&gt;Dawnstar Spire&lt;/a&gt;.\nBloodvalor sent &lt;a href=\"Sangrias%20Stillblade\"&gt;Sangrias Stillblade&lt;/a&gt; and the blood elf &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt; to their First Trial. While the adventurer won and killed Stillblade, this was plan of the training. As the adventurer was preparing for Sangrias' resurrection, Bloodvalor sent a group of initiates to retrieve his body.\nFollowing the death of &lt;a href=\"Tirion%20Fordring\"&gt;Tirion Fordring&lt;/a&gt;, Bloodvalor joined the &lt;a href=\"Silver%20Hand\"&gt;Silver Hand&lt;/a&gt; and is located in the &lt;a href=\"Sanctum%20of%20Light\"&gt;Sanctum of Light&lt;/a&gt;.\nFollowing the split of the Order during the &lt;a href=\"Fourth%20War\"&gt;Fourth War&lt;/a&gt;, he is no longer a member of the Silver Hand.\nAfter the death of &lt;a href=\"Vorath\"&gt;Vorath&lt;/a&gt;, Bloodvalor was among the gathered paladins outside the &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Blood\"&gt;Hall of Blood&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Farstriders%27%20Square\"&gt;Farstriders' Square&lt;/a&gt; to congratulate the &lt;a href=\"Adventurer\"&gt;sin'dorei hero&lt;/a&gt; for their victory in &lt;a href=\"Deatholme\"&gt;Deatholme&lt;/a&gt;.\nQuotes.\nWelcome to the headquarters of the Blood Knights, the defenders of Quel'Thalas, the faithful servants of Silvermoon, and the true masters of the Light."}
